{"tid":1633912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各勇武小組應該要自己建立聯合行動機制, 唔好再睇連登/TG channel去決定行動先可以做到真正遊擊","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:06:28.000Z","uid":69526,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"92b5c22cc1026d937f342d008db405b42a24f1f6","tid":1633912,"uid":69526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"老實講大家都知連登/Channel一定有帶風/mon post鬼/狗<br />\n<br />\n各勇武小組要開始自己建立<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一啲你地自己建立嘅通訊方式</strong></span>去組織行動, 即係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你地自己決定行動嘅時地人</span></strong></span>, 唔係再等連登啲所謂嘅共識, 先可以真正避開啲狗佈定防等你地黎而失去手足. 每次失去一個都係太多. <br />\n<br />\n但一定要係幾個幾個小隊行動, 以免一個快閃太小人而失敗/唔夠support/冇人睇水<br />\n<br />\n如果你地想等和理非, 當然可以留意下佢地打算出現嘅時間而等佢地幫你聲東擊西, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但你地自己嘅行動方式/時機絕對唔需要講出黎</span></strong></span>,  你地自己知就可以, 如果你地夾到幾個小隊, 其實零晨都可以做<br />\n<br />\n總之<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n祝 武運亨通"},{"pid":"b1470bb556b114af36c3bd91687a277c0a0ce800","tid":1633912,"uid":69526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"認同請推<br />\n記住對準政權"},{"pid":"100e3b4990d5b89c21ad7e079462365040ef36c1","tid":1633912,"uid":69526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3939b1ee74454d2978c7998deceb8881470d015","tid":1633912,"uid":69526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:51:43.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeec7582187904e24e042d2095eb3fdb7bce8ca5","tid":1633912,"uid":69526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eddd9da54968bb8a4baffb9057ca9b26dd2a09e","tid":1633912,"uid":69526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"